headline: Bitcoin, XRP Prices Rise After Crypto Bill Talks. Why It’s Not Enough for a Rally.
summary: Crypto prices may have been responding to policy news—there were tentative signs of progress on a digital asset bill known as the Clarity Act.  The White House held a meeting Thursday between groups representing crypto firms and banks.  Digital asset investors certainly need more.
